+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+

markbuttons adds four Mark as: buttons to the bottom of the message list:
Mark as: Read, Unread, Flagged, UnFlagged

Installation
------------
Add the plugin to your config/main.inc.php

Configuration
-------------
None.

Localization
------------
The button hints use the default labels from the main roundcube
localization files.
I have added a number of languages for the 'Mark:' label that precedes
the buttons, let me know if a language is incorrect, or if you
have a language that is currently supported by roundcube that I should add.

